Comment: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:35.66,On Top,,0,0,0,,KUROZUMI SEMIMARU - BIWA PLAYING PRIEST | BIWA PLAYING PRIEST KUROZUMI SEMIMARU
Comment: 0,0:08:58.39,0:09:01.93,MainLow,,0,0,0,,KUROZUMI HIGURASHI - AN OLD WOMAN | OLD HAG KUROZUMI HIGURASHI
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:07.56,Main,,0,0,0,,The Roger Pirates are disbanded!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:15.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After reaching the last island, Laugh Tale,\Nthe Roger Pirates disbanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:21.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Oden, who returned to the Wano Country,\Nlearned that Orochi is sitting as the Shogun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:28.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I understand the way Orochi does things!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:33.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Guys! Protect my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:36.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Oden-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:40.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Protect Kuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:53.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Oden-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:56.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you going to attack Orochi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:03.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Toki, you don't have to be afraid anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.75,0:03:06.37,Main,,0,0,0,,No! Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:08.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Orochi will stop at nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:13.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I know how you feel,\Nbut it is too dangerous to charge in with no plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:17.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll leave Kuri to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:27.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,I don't understand complicated things,\Nbut I think this is what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:30.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,A fool took over the Wano Country!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:32.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,With the help of a strong pirate,...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:37.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,a weak fool took advantage of the period of isolation\Nduring which no one would intervene...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,...and is trying to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:52.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,...turn this country into hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:00.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:04.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:07.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Be merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:24.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,It's a beautiful country...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:27.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,I won't let him turn it into hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:42.17,Main,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:43.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:47.21,Main,,0,0,0,,It's an emergency!\NKozuki Oden is heading toward the Flower Capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:49.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Report to Orochi-sama immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:57.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Orochi-sama! Please respond! Orochi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:08.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Was that...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:09.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Oden-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:12.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Oden-sama has returned?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:13.97,Main,,0,0,0,,He's the true heir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.97,0:05:16.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Will he become the Shogun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:21.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Orochi's dominion will end!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:25.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Leave, Kozuki Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:28.68,Main,,0,0,0,,This is Shogun Orochi-sama's castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:32.10,Main,,0,0,0,,You cannot enter without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:05.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Shogun Orochi! Please evacuate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:08.59,Main,,0,0,0,,What? What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:12.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Kozuki Oden invaded the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:13.68,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:25.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Orochi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.89,0:06:28.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Orochi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:32.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Orochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:35.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Orochi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:40.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Orochi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:51.26,Main,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a minute! Oden-sa... O-Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:56.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Think twice!\NIf you cut me up, Kaido won't just take it lying down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:07:01.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Think what'll happen to this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:05.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:10.20,Main,,0,0,0,,After I slice you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:16.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,I forgot... he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:22.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,He's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:31.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Orochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:34.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:07:59.87,Main,,0,0,0,,What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:02.33,Main,,0,0,0,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:06.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it glass?! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:12.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Come out, Orochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:17.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Orochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:24.73,Main,,0,0,0,,No need to be scared, Orochi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:31.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Trust my Bari Bari technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:41.41,Main,,0,0,0,,In theory,\Nmy barriers won't allow anyone to come closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:45.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Your strength means nothing, Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:49.42,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:53.51,Main,,0,0,0,,If you were a pirate,\NI'm sure you're really familiar with...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:58.26,Main,,0,0,0,,...the superhuman powers of the Devil Fruits!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:04.14,Main,,0,0,0,,So you're a power-user!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:09.90,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NPeople in this country call them magic-users...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:20.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Oden, if anger and violence were the answer,...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:23.70,Main,,0,0,0,,...the Daimyos from other regions \Nwould already have done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:26.62,Main,,0,0,0,,No one can kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:33.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Orochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:43.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Orochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:51.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I heard, for whatever reason,\Nmy father named you as a proxy Shogun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:54.44,Main,,0,0,0,,...until my return!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:04.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, yield the throne to me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:07.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I wasn't going to become such a big shot,...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:11.46,Main,,0,0,0,,...but I can make it a somewhat \Nbetter country than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:18.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, unfortunately,...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:22.39,Main,,0,0,0,,...that's not what your father, Sukiyaki, said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:25.27,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:33.61,Main,,0,0,0,,It's good to have you back, Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:35.44,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! Father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:37.19,Main,,0,0,0,,How are you alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:44.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Who the Daimyos and all the \Nother fools believed was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:46.91,Main,,0,0,0,,...me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:51.58,Main,,0,0,0,,They believed a lie from this old hag\Nwho transformed herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:53.84,Translation Info,,0,0,0,,マネマネの実 Mane Mane no Mi, \NClone-Clone Fruit (Imitation)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:53.84,Main,,0,0,0,,...with the Mane Mane no Mi power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:11:00.76,Main,,0,0,0,,The whole country believed it\Nand let me have the Shogun's post!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:04.85,Main,,0,0,0,,So I don't have to switch positions with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:11.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Now there's no way to know\Nwhat the real Sukiyaki was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:14.57,Main,,0,0,0,,What did you do to my father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:18.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Did he really die of an illness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:39.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That day, upon the crowd that was looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:42.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...up at the castle cheering for \Nthe return of the Kozuki Family,...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:45.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...poisoned arrows rained down from nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:49.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Two people were wounded\Nand lost their sight after a bout of bloody vomit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:52.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The other townspeople\Nwho took shelter in the disarray...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:12:01.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...saw a big dragon\Nup in the darkened sky of the capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:11.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He grew up as a wild man, but he became the Daimyo of Kuri and went out to sea,...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:15.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...and matched up evenly with\Nthe world's greatest pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:25.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Then, he returned home\Nhaving become a lot stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:29.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The invincible Kozuki Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:36.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NOden-sama will save this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:38.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Oden-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:41.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Oden-sama! We were waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:43.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Oden-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:49.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was expected to become a savior for the people\Nwho suffered the power of evil...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:53.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Oden-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:56.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A few hours later, Kozuki Oden...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:13:00.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...stripped himself down\Nin front of the Shogun Orochi's castle...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:08.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...and acted like a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:35.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I knew you could do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:46.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, radish, ganmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:50.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Chikuwa and eggs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:56.56,Main,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, go ahead and eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:59.61,Main,,0,0,0,,If it didn't boil...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:04.03,Main,,0,0,0,,...it wouldn't be Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:10.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Orochi and Kaido's subordinates \Nlaughed at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:18.54,Main,,0,0,0,,One, two, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:25.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Having groveled in the dirt and earned\Na small amount of money, the big man went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:33.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Wano Country's true \Nheir, Kozuki Oden's return...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:37.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...was the nation's last hope, so to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:41.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But people were completely let down\Nand deeply disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:47.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And eventually, they even became angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:54.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Kuri's silly lord, Kozuki Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:58.83,Main,,0,0,0,,The snake's stare petrified him with terror!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:02.75,Main,,0,0,0,,If you laugh, you lose! Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:08.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Konbu, important!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:12.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Konbu is important!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:18.23,Main,,0,0,0,,The essential factor for \Nthe taste is the stock!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:20.60,Main,,0,0,0,,If it didn't boil...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:25.57,Main,,0,0,0,,...it wouldn't be Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:29.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Oden showed up in the capital once a week,...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:32.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...and clowned around in front of the castle\Nto earn a small amount of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:35.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even on rainy days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:38.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Or windy days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:40.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Or snowy days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:48.71,Main,,0,0,0,,We are begging you, Oden-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:51.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Please tell us the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:57.76,Main,,0,0,0,,What did you and Orochi talk about?!\NWhy are you doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:16:03.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Even the people of Kuri who believed in you all this time\Nfinally gave up on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:09.57,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:12.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I dance naked and get paid every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:15.49,Main,,0,0,0,,That's my job!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:19.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Word of his strange behavior in the capital\Ntraveled to Kuri, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:25.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Daikon, ganmo, chikuwa and eggs!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:29.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Konnyaku, chikuwabu, hanpen, potatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:34.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't forget shirataki noodles, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:39.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't be a man like him! Pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:44.23,Main,,0,0,0,,If you become Orochi's dog,\Ncut your belly like a samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:48.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Konbu, important! Life, important!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:52.95,Main,,0,0,0,,The essential factor for \Nthe taste is the stock!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:03.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A year later...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:08.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:11.55,Main,,0,0,0,,The Shogun's messenger brought this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:13.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:16.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:32.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Roger...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:36.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:39.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,People's dreams... The tide of the times...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:48.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,As long as people seek the answer of freedom,...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:51.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,...these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:18:01.39,Past,,0,0,0,,Did you say that you're gonna die soon,\NRoger?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:05.73,Past,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's only a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:15.44,Past,,0,0,0,,Do you know what people of the World Government\Ncall me these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:19.03,Past,,0,0,0,,"Gold Roger."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:24.04,Past,,0,0,0,,What? Is that your real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:25.83,Past,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:30.25,Past,,0,0,0,,My name is Gol D. Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:34.50,Past,,0,0,0,,I meet people with "D" \Nin their names sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:42.18,Past,,0,0,0,,I have a crew member who has it.\NHis name is Teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:45.97,Past,,0,0,0,,What does "D" stand for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:50.73,Past,,0,0,0,,Ah, do you wanna know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:57.75,Past,,0,0,0,,Alright, I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:19:00.50,Past,,0,0,0,,It's a story from way back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:07.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After receiving a foreign newspaper\Nfrom the Shogun Orochi, Oden...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:41.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...ran along the seacoast,\Ncried out loud, then, laughed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:44.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...and cried again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:53.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:53.64,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, let's get this over with quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.41,0:21:11.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:14.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Where did you hide all \Nthe treasure you found?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:18.96,Main,,0,0,0,,You got it, didn't you?!\NThat legendary treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:23.13,Main,,0,0,0,,That great treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.13,0:21:26.62,Main,,0,0,0,,The One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:38.73,Main,,0,0,0,,My treasure?\NIf you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:40.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:48.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I left everything this \Nworld has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:02.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,24 years before the present day,...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:07.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...the world went wild over the execution of\Nthe King of the Pirates, Gold Roger,...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.36,0:22:10.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...and to get the enormous wealth...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.43,0:22:14.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...and the great treasure of\Nthe One Piece he left behind,...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.18,0:22:18.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...all sorts of people took to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:24.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That was the beginning \Nof the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.46,0:22:41.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:47.17,Main,,0,0,0,,You're unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.34,0:22:54.64,Main,,0,0,0,,You lived quite a life!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:10.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Orochi's nefarious plan is revealed!\N He uses any means necessary...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.95,0:23:14.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...for his evildoing and Oden \Nfinally erupts in anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.95,0:23:16.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To save the country,...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.49,0:23:20.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...Oden and the Akazaya members face\NKaido, their domination-plotting nemesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.67,0:23:25.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The legendary raid that will go down to\Nposterity is about to be launched!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.88,0:23:27.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Next time on One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.25,0:23:30.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Raid! \NOden and the Akazaya Nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.70,0:23:33.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
